metadata.name: Town with an Ocean View
metadata.description:
Weather forecast predicts clear blue skies all week long
You find yourself exploring through the town's narrow alleyways
You could see that the town is taking it easy today
Leisurely enjoying a fine summer's day

Inspired by the works of Studio Ghibly and Joe Hisaishi

Auction winner will get a signed 1/1 print

Hand painted digitally
3840 x 2160 px
